Release Notes for Version 3.12.2
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.12.2 is the 3rd release in
the Errata Tool 3.12 development period. It closes [38 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release of Errata Tool includes a redesigned create/edit advisory form,
support for managing docker package lists and tags, multi-advisory pub pushes,
pre-pushing content to RHN &amp; CDN, plus a number of bug fixes and
improvements.

Additionally, during the 3.12.2 development period, an additional [3 bug
fixes][hotfixes] were shipped in 3.12.1.2.

